"directories":{}}},"readme":"# find-root\nrecursively find the closest package.json\n\n## usage\nSay you want to check if the directory name of a project matches its\nmodule name in package.json:\n\n```js\nvar path = require('path')\nvar findRoot = require('find-root')\n\n// from a starting directory, recursively search for the nearest\n// directory containing package.json\nvar root = findRoot('/Users/jden/dev/find-root/tests')\n// => '/Users/jden/dev/find-root'\n\nvar dirname = path.basename(root)\nconsole.log('is it the same?')\nconsole.log(dirname === require(path.join(root, 'package.json')).name)\n```\n\n\n## api\n\n### `findRoot: (startingPath : String) => String`\n\nReturns the path for the nearest directory to `startingPath` containing\na `package.json` file, eg `/foo/module`.\n\nThrows an error if no `package.json` is found at any level in the\n`startingPath`.\n\n\n## installation\n\n    $ npm install find-root\n\n\n## running the tests\n\nFrom package root:\n\n    $ npm install\n    $ npm test\n\n\n## contributors\n\n- jden <jason@denizac.org>\n\n\n## license\nMIT. (c) MMXIII AgileMD http://agilemd.com\n","maintainers":[{"name":"jden","email":"jason@denizac.org"}],"time":{"modified":"2015-04-14T17:21:01.999Z","created":"2013-12-05T21:36:50.922Z","0.1.0":"2013-12-05T21:36:51.954Z","0.1.1":"2013-12-05T21:57:44.408Z"},"author":{"name":"AgileMD","email":"hello@agilemd.com"},"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git@github.com:agilemd/find-root.git"},"readmeFilename":"README.md","users":{"itonyyo":true,"codedsignal":true},"homepage":"https://github.com/agilemd/find-root","keywords":["package","module","base","root"],"contributors":[{"name":"jden","email":"jason@denizac.org"}],"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/agilemd/find-root/issues"},"license":"MIT","_attachments":{},"_etag":"\"41YN7SFX5IQE3YBX87A1SO6W3\""}